<span class="displaytext">arlington, va -- u.s. senator (candidate full) today issued the following statement on <i>district of columbia v. heller:</i><p>"today, the supreme court will hear oral arguments on <i>district of columbia v. heller,</i>a landmark case for all americans who believe as i do that the second amendment guarantees an individual right to keep and bear arms. i am proud to have joined in an amicus brief to the court calling for a ruling in keeping with the clear intent of our founding fathers, which ensures the second amendment rights of the residents of district of columbia are reaffirmed."</p></span>



